        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Netflix 称用户平均每日看 2 小时　全球用户人数突破 2.8 亿</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/netflix-says-subscribers-spend-two-hours-a-day-on-the-platform/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=netflix-says-subscribers-spend-two-hours-a-day-on-the-platform</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/netflix-says-subscribers-spend-two-hours-a-day-on-the-platform/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 12:00:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影视娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Netflix]]>
            </category>
